5. Server Configuration:
```apache
# Apache configuration for optimal serving
<Files "login-bg.jpg">
    Header set Cache-Control "public, max-age=31536000, immutable"
    Header set Vary "Accept-Encoding"
</Files>
```

6. Image Processing Commands:
```bash
# Generate optimized JPEG
convert login-bg-source.jpg \
    -strip \
    -interlace Plane \
    -quality 85 \
    -colorspace sRGB \
    -resize 1920x1080 \
    login-bg.jpg

# Generate WebP variant
cwebp -q 85 login-bg.jpg -o login-bg.webp

# Generate responsive variants
convert login-bg.jpg -resize 1280x720 login-bg-tablet.jpg
convert login-bg.jpg -resize 640x360 login-bg-mobile.jpg